Interface HttpClientResponse

  • All Superinterfaces:
    HttpClientInfos, HttpInfos

    public interface HttpClientResponse
extends HttpClientInfos
    An HttpClient Reactive metadata contract for incoming response. It inherits several accessor related to HTTP flow : headers, params, URI, method, websocket...
